at his side dukakis told a news conference on capitol hill that he 
was unable to reach jackson by telephone tuesday morning to notify 
him of his vice presidential decision 
as a result jackson did not learn of the choice until asked 
about it by reporters when he arrived at washingtons national 
airport 
